Get started with Fifteen_

Step 1

Import your sources

Drop links, PDFs, docs, and notes into a datapack. Fifteen organizes what matters.

Step 2

Draft your memo

Start from a template or a prompt. Generate sections as patches with citations.

Step 3

Review and share

Accept diffs, add comments, export, and share a clean IC-ready version.

What is Fifteen?

Fifteen is an agentic workspace built for investors and research-heavy teams. Capture sources, draft memos with context-aware agents, and keep decisions traceable from first signal to IC.
